item.title: Starting 2016
item.description: A quick introduction: I’m really excited to start this blog, for a few reasons as you’ll see, but I wanted to first preface this with saying: don’t worry, this isn’t just a “New Year’s Resolution Blog ™”. As some of you may know, I am currently in San Francisco, officially. I flew here on December 31, so I welcomed 2016 in my new, partially set up apartment. I moved out here for the time-being to pursue a Software Engineer Fellowship at Hackbright.
